project_descr: The Project aims to improve the working modalities between the UN and the MoGCDSW and ensure better coordination, harmonization, reduced transaction costs and duplication of activities for the Ministry's efficient and effective service delivery.

outputs.output_descr: Capacity of Public and Private Sector institutions and CSOs strengthened to mainstream gender in all sectors to achieve gender equality and improve political and economic empowerment of women in Malawi.
